flowRoot.flowPara: 1. Go to NAU Building 90 (School of Informatics, Computing, and Cyber Systems) which is on S. Knoles Dr. between W. Riordan Rd. and W. University Dr. (behind buildings 56 and 54).
2. From the main entrance take the hallway on the right. Dr Hocking's office is at the end, past the cubicles. (Room 120)
